// All authors with book and second counts
MATCH (s:Section)--(b:Book)--(a:Author)
//WHERE b.dateUploaded.year = 2024
RETURN 
	'https://librivox.org/author/'+a.id AS url,
	trim(COALESCE(a.firstName, '') + ' ' + COALESCE(a.lastName, '')) AS author,
	COALESCE(a.birthDate, '') + '-' + COALESCE(a.deathDate, '') AS life,
	COUNT(DISTINCT b) AS books,
    SUM(s.playtime) AS playtime
ORDER BY playtime DESC
